M5StackSideBB Requirements.

 

Remove redundant copper from the spacer PCB.

 
 
 
Adjust the hole positions of the spacer PCB and the main PCB, then solder to join them.
 

After that solder header to top, socket to bottom.

 

 

 

Put pin sockets for inside of PCB as well as possible.

 
 

Finish images
